        },
        {
            "title": "恒指升幅擴大至逾800點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股尾市升幅持續擴大，恒指升逾800點，較早時報23392點，升815點，升幅3.61%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科技指數升近6%，報5819點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14723326-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7%e8%87%b3%e9%80%be800%e9%bb%9e-4",
